{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/infinity/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Aksharaa's Stories","author":"Aksharaasri A"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"58670581-73c7-57d9-94b3-7af92d9e4377","excerpt":"One day a baby number \"8\" was born to mother \"8\" and father \"8\". Baby \"8\" was a very good child.\nBut he soon came to know that baby \"8\" will only live for…","html":"<p>One day a baby number \"8\" was born to mother \"8\" and father \"8\". Baby \"8\" was a very good child.\nBut he soon came to know that baby \"8\" will only live for 8 days. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 970px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7a2c772a85897d42630bdf86afae7478/c35b6/parents.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 135.3909465020576%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Parents\"\n        title=\"Parents\"\n        src=\"/static/7a2c772a85897d42630bdf86afae7478/ec7ce/parents.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7a2c772a85897d42630bdf86afae7478/3f316/parents.jpg 243w,\n/static/7a2c772a85897d42630bdf86afae7478/0d3a1/parents.jpg 485w,\n/static/7a2c772a85897d42630bdf86afae7478/ec7ce/parents.jpg 970w,\n/static/7a2c772a85897d42630bdf86afae7478/8010b/parents.jpg 1455w,\n/static/7a2c772a85897d42630bdf86afae7478/f32bc/parents.jpg 1940w,\n/static/7a2c772a85897d42630bdf86afae7478/c35b6/parents.jpg 2572w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Baby \"8\" loved his parents very much and thought I want to live long with my parents. </p>\n<p>So baby \"8\" thought for a long time and then got an idea. </p>\n<p>He went to the mountain and asked. </p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Mountain... Mountain... Please can you make me live long?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 970px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/24006f6f4ff36d3480bf36311c51cc14/7e626/asks-mountain.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 140.74074074074073%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Mountain\"\n        title=\"Mountain\"\n        src=\"/static/24006f6f4ff36d3480bf36311c51cc14/ec7ce/asks-mountain.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/24006f6f4ff36d3480bf36311c51cc14/3f316/asks-mountain.jpg 243w,\n/static/24006f6f4ff36d3480bf36311c51cc14/0d3a1/asks-mountain.jpg 485w,\n/static/24006f6f4ff36d3480bf36311c51cc14/ec7ce/asks-mountain.jpg 970w,\n/static/24006f6f4ff36d3480bf36311c51cc14/8010b/asks-mountain.jpg 1455w,\n/static/24006f6f4ff36d3480bf36311c51cc14/f32bc/asks-mountain.jpg 1940w,\n/static/24006f6f4ff36d3480bf36311c51cc14/7e626/asks-mountain.jpg 2443w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>I'm sorry, I cannot help you. See the sky, there is Sun. He will help you, </p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>said the mountain.</p>\n<p>Baby \"8\" goes to meet the Sun and asks</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Sun... Sun... Can you please make me live long?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Hmmmmm!!!, </p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>thought the Sun.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Then I'll make you Infinity, </p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>said the Sun.</p>\n<p>He cut the arms, legs and eyes of baby \"8\" and put the baby \"8\" in sleeping line.\nThen he put back it's arms, legs and eyes.  </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 970px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6385ac099e6a8ced33681a963f73ed35/dbfa0/becomes-infinity.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 142.38683127572017%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"infinity\"\n        title=\"infinity\"\n        src=\"/static/6385ac099e6a8ced33681a963f73ed35/ec7ce/becomes-infinity.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6385ac099e6a8ced33681a963f73ed35/3f316/becomes-infinity.jpg 243w,\n/static/6385ac099e6a8ced33681a963f73ed35/0d3a1/becomes-infinity.jpg 485w,\n/static/6385ac099e6a8ced33681a963f73ed35/ec7ce/becomes-infinity.jpg 970w,\n/static/6385ac099e6a8ced33681a963f73ed35/8010b/becomes-infinity.jpg 1455w,\n/static/6385ac099e6a8ced33681a963f73ed35/f32bc/becomes-infinity.jpg 1940w,\n/static/6385ac099e6a8ced33681a963f73ed35/dbfa0/becomes-infinity.jpg 2467w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Now baby \"8\" became baby \"∞\" and lived happily for ever.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Infinity","date":"2020, Jun 14","moral":"If you are good, good things will happen to you.","tags":null,"img":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"aspectRatio":0.7110091743119266,"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","sizes":"(max-width: 2443px) 100vw, 2443px","src":"/static/24006f6f4ff36d3480bf36311c51cc14/64e78/asks-mountain.jpg","srcSet":"/static/24006f6f4ff36d3480bf36311c51cc14/2f037/asks-mountain.jpg 930w,\n/static/24006f6f4ff36d3480bf36311c51cc14/23f4e/asks-mountain.jpg 1860w,\n/static/24006f6f4ff36d3480bf36311c51cc14/64e78/asks-mountain.jpg 2443w"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/infinity/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/tree-branch/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Tree Branch","img":null}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/the-bad-and-the-good/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"The Bad and The Good","img":null}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2865365438","63159454"]}